    store64(p + PROF_SPIRIT, "Healing is precision, not gentleness alone. You know the body's grammar well enough to rewrite it in silver. But your tradition also remembers your jealousy of your son's greater art -- a reminder that the healer's pride is the wound hardest to mend.");
